Rosslyn Chapel,

79
0:03:43.26,000 --> 0:03:45,000
Pompeii,

80
0:03:45.26,000 --> 0:03:47,000
and our latest project, Mt. Rushmore,

81
0:03:47.26,000 --> 0:03:49,000
which happened to be one of

82
0:03:49.26,000 --> 0:03:51,000
our most challenging projects.

83
0:03:51.26,000 --> 0:03:53,000
As you see here, we had to develop

84
0:03:53.26,000 --> 0:03:56,000
a special rig to bring the scanner

85
0:03:56.26,000 --> 0:03:59,000
up close and personal.

